  <description>
    <p>
      Crucible gives you a clear overview of your system hardware and lets you
      push it to its limits with built-in stress testing.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>View CPU, GPU, and memory details at a glance</li>
      <li>Copy a spec sheet to share with others</li>
      <li>Run CPU stress tests with configurable duration</li>
      <li>Monitor temperature and usage in real time</li>
      <li>Automatic safety cutoff when temperatures get too high</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
